{"tid":608253,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗自拍隨時犯法","createTime":"2018-03-28T03:45:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-28T07:12:50.000Z","uid":54373,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ce2ef251c649ebc66c31190cc553c32ca0d7cd45","tid":608253,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T03:45:44.000Z","msg":"皇家馬德里球星基斯坦奴朗拿度一向鍾意自拍，但最近一張自拍相隨時令佢惹上官非。<br />\n事緣C朗近日就係社交網站貼上一張自拍照，相中除左有佢靚仔大頭之外，背景仲影到「車來車往」，明顯係揸緊車時影。根據西班牙法例，駕駛其間使用手提電話等設備屬違法，要罰款200歐元。雖然200歐元對C朗嚟講唔係錢，但「明張目膽」咁犯法始終對形象唔係幾好，而且揸車時分心影相隨時害人害己﹐大家千祈唔好學。<br />\n<br />\n#傷人<br />\n#逃稅<br />\n#強姦<br />\n#衰11<br />\n#超速<br />\n#開淫P<br />\n#斷背<br />\n#恐嚇<br />\n#勒索<br />\n#衝紅燈<br />\n#非禮<br />\n#性騷擾<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">#危險駕駛</span>"},{"pid":"a7f73757cb755c34695d869080918ffb50768c37","tid":608253,"uid":3161,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T03:50:54.000Z","msg":"你知唔知佢賣一張親筆簽名自拍相 可以幫到幾多山區小朋友"},{"pid":"3a3f6d33d75a7de021a4530d0757df983fc8ca4c","tid":608253,"uid":12503,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"a7f73757cb755c34695d869080918ffb50768c37","tid":608253,"uid":3161,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T03:50:54.000Z","msg":"你知唔知佢賣一張親筆簽名自拍相 可以幫到幾多山區小朋友"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T03:53:44.000Z","msg":"你知唔知佢賣一張冇違法嘅親筆簽名自拍相 一樣可以幫到好多山區小朋友"},{"pid":"c7cf5b97857ec20146f89dbfbb3528b6fcfddae8","tid":608253,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T03:54:49.000Z","msg":"偽善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n場內場外小花都贏幾條街"},{"pid":"a6d7d534ce34340b765d6b9f1a44c9f1846eb00a","tid":608253,"uid":44678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c7cf5b97857ec20146f89dbfbb3528b6fcfddae8","tid":608253,"uid":27485,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-28T03:54:49.000Z","msg":"偽善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji